---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import HeroSecondary from "@/components/hero-secondary.astro";
import { HeartIcon, GiftTopIcon, GiftIcon } from '@heroicons/vue/24/outline';
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Dance1 from "@/assets/kamotion-02.jpeg";
import Dance2 from "@/assets/kamotion-03.jpeg";
import Dance3 from "@/assets/kamotion-04.jpg";
---

<Layout title="DaysArts volunteer benefits">
  <!-- HeroSecondary text structure
    title case
    sentence case
    sentence case
  -->
  <HeroSecondary
    tagline="Non-competitive dance for all abilities"
    title="Dance, fitness & fun at Kamotion"
    content="A DaysArts society program">
  </HeroSecondary>


    <!-- background -->
    <div class="relative overflow-x-clip mt-10">
      <div class="absolute -top-80 left-[max(6rem,33%)] -z-10 transform-gpu blur-3xl sm:left-1/2 md:top-20 lg:ml-20 xl:top-3 xl:ml-56" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="aspect-[801/1036] w-[50.0625rem] bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#ff80b5] to-[#9089fc] opacity-30" style="clip-path: polygon(63.1% 29.6%, 100% 17.2%, 76.7% 3.1%, 48.4% 0.1%, 44.6% 4.8%, 54.5% 25.4%, 59.8% 49.1%, 55.3% 57.9%, 44.5% 57.3%, 27.8% 48%, 35.1% 81.6%, 0% 97.8%, 39.3% 100%, 35.3% 81.5%, 97.2% 52.8%, 63.1% 29.6%)" />
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
          <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">At Kamotion Dance Group,</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-700">We believe in the joy and enrichment that dance brings to people of all ages. Established in 2017, we've been providing a vibrant and fun-filled atmosphere for children to learn the basics of dance and for adults to indulge in dance-inspired fitness classes. Our classes are crafted to foster a love for movement and creativity, while also focusing on the benefits of physical fitness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:mt-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-12">
          <div class="relative lg:order-last lg:col-span-5">
            <svg class="absolute -top-[40rem] left-1 -z-10 h-[64rem] w-[175.5rem] -translate-x-1/2 stroke-gray-900/10 [mask-image:radial-gradient(64rem_64rem_at_111.5rem_0%,white,transparent)]" aria-hidden="true">
              <defs>
                <pattern id="e87443c8-56e4-4c20-9111-55b82fa704e3" width="200" height="200" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                  <path d="M0.5 0V200M200 0.5L0 0.499983" />
                </pattern>
              </defs>
              <rect width="100%" height="100%" stroke-width="0" fill="url(#e87443c8-56e4-4c20-9111-55b82fa704e3)" />
            </svg>
            <figure class="border-l border-indigo-600 pl-8">
              <blockquote class="text-xl font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900">
                <p>“When you dance, your purpose is not to get a certain place on the floor, it's to enjoy every step along the way.”</p>
              </blockquote>
              <figcaption class="mt-8 flex gap-x-4">
                <div class="text-sm leading-6">
                  <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Wayne Dyer</div>
                </div>
              </figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
          <div class="max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-700 lg:col-span-7">
            <p>The purpose of the Kamotion Dance Group is to be an affordable, accessible, and inclusive group for children to learn the basics of dance in a fun, non-competitive atmosphere. Since 2017, we have also offered dance-inspired fitness classes for adults in order to provide an opportunity to maintain health and fitness close to home in the company of friends and neighbours.</p>

            <p class="mt-4">Classes are one or two nights per week for 10-week sessions plus a recital per session. Winter session runs January to March and Fall session runs September to December. Ballet, tap, and preschool learn to dance classes are offered with opportunity for additional classes as interest dictates, as well as adult dance-inspired fitness classes.</p>

            <p class="mt-4">We are a volunteer-run, not-for-profit group which allows for low cost to participants. There are no additional costs (such as costumes) to the registration fee.</p>

            <ul role="list" class="mt-8 max-w-xl space-y-8 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <HeartIcon class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900">$50</strong> Per session for 30 minute classes.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <GiftIcon class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900">$75</strong> Per session for 45 minute classes.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <GiftTopIcon class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900">$100</strong> Per session for 60 minute classes.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="my-4 flex justify-center gap-5 py-4 sm:gap-8">
              <div class="relative aspect-[9/10] w-44 flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 sm:w-72 sm:rounded-xl rotate-2">
                  <Image
                  src={Dance1}
                  format="avif"
                  quality="mid"
                  width={1024}
                  height={1024 * 1.5}
                  alt="Kamotion dance students"
                  class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2 rounded-lg"
                />
              </div>

              <div class="relative aspect-[9/10] w-44 flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 sm:w-72 sm:rounded-xl -rotate-2">
                <Image
                src={Dance2}
                format="avif"
                quality="mid"
                width={1024}
                height={1024 * 1.5}
                alt="Kamotion dance students"
                class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2 rounded-lg"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="relative aspect-[9/10] w-44 flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 sm:w-72 sm:rounded-xl rotate-2">
              <Image
              src={Dance3}
              format="avif"
              quality="mid"
              width={1024}
              height={1024 * 1.5}
              alt="Kamotion dance students"
              class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2 rounded-lg"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

            <h2 class="mt-16 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Immerse Yourself in the World of Performing Arts</h2>

            <p class="mt-6">Non-competitive, inclusive dance group for kids ages 4 to adult to learn the basics of dance. For more information see the <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100079928076398" target="_blank" class="whitespace-nowrap text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Kamotion Dance Facebook page</a> or contact Alison Eshpeter at <a href="tel:7802711145" itemprop="telephone" class="whitespace-nowrap font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-600 hover:underline">780-271-1145</a></p>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

